QuestData.Title: Down in the Deeps
QuestData.Description: Well, friend, if Pozzik wants you to have your own boat, the first thing we're going to need is parts. Now guess who gets to go get them?$B$B<Razzeric smiles as he points downward and then grabs you a spare diving helm and flippers.>$B$BI'm afraid so, $n. You get to go down into the deeps and salvage what rocket car parts you can find at the Raceway Ruins.
QuestData.CompletionText: We can get started as soon as you get everything that's on the list.
